OL,3,CMan jailed for scamming in-laws by
OL,4,Cforging contract with Paris Saint-
OL,5,CGermain
OL,7,FA "grandiose narcissist" who pretended
OL,8,Fto have a business deal with Paris
OL,9,FSaint-Germain has been jailed, after
OL,10,Fscamming his in-laws and a company out
OL,11,Fof more than #3m.
OL,13,FEdward Blackmore claimed his company,
OL,14,FOGC Sport Investments, had agreed a
OL,15,Fmulti-million-pound services contract
OL,16,Fwith the top league French football
OL,17,Fclub in August 2018.
