OL,3,CMan jailed for scamming in-laws by
OL,4,Cforging contract with Paris Saint-
OL,5,CGermain
OL,7,FThe 45-year-old forged the stamp and
OL,8,Fsignature of a lawyer to make the
OL,9,Fcontract believable, and used it to
OL,10,Fsecure an interest-free loan from his
OL,11,Fin-laws of #1.8m.
OL,13,FBlackmore, from Holt in Wiltshire,
OL,14,Fused this money to buy a Grade-II
OL,15,Flisted home in Widcombe, Bath and
OL,16,Fassured his in-laws that it would be
OL,17,Frepaid "shortly".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
