OL,3,CMan jailed for scamming in-laws by
OL,4,Cforging contract with Paris Saint-
OL,5,CGermain
OL,7,FHe also failed to pay back the finance
OL,8,Fcompany, stumping up just #76,000 in
OL,9,Fthree monthly payments.
OL,11,FThe failure to pay off his loans led
OL,12,Fto Blackmore, his wife and their young
OL,13,Fchildren to be evicted from their
OL,14,Fhouse, which was sold to repay the
OL,15,Ffinance company's loan.
OL,17,FBut Blackmore's in-laws have not been
OL,18,Fpaid back. They reported him to Action
OL,19,FFraud, who then referred the cased to
OL,20,FWiltshire Police.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
