OL,4,Cforging contract with Paris Saint-
OL,5,CGermain
OL,7,FHe was then charged and pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto three counts of fraud by false
OL,9,Frepresentation: two relating to
OL,10,Ffraudulent claims against his in-laws
OL,11,Fand one against the finance company.
OL,13,FBlackmore was jailed for six years and
OL,14,Feight months at a hearing at Swindon
OL,15,FCrown Court on 21 February.
