OL,7,F"My husband has worked hard his entire
OL,8,Fworking life and we had plans for our
OL,9,Fretirement. We had dreams of 'our
OL,10,Ftime' ` travelling the world together,
OL,11,Ftreating our children and
OL,12,Fgrandchildren, and making memories. Mr
OL,13,FBlackmore has denied us of this.
OL,15,F"Mr Blackmore's total lack of remorse,
OL,16,Frespect, explanation or apology is
OL,17,Fsimply incomprehensible to us, and
OL,18,Ftotally unacceptable.
