OL,7,FIn a statement, she said: "When I
OL,8,Fexchanged wedding vows, I believed I
OL,9,Fwas entering a partnership built on
OL,10,Ftrust, honesty and mutual respect.
OL,11,FInstead, I became the victim of a
OL,12,Fcalculated betrayal that has shattered
OL,13,Fmy life.
OL,15,F"The financial damage has been
OL,16,Fdevastating. Before I got married, I
OL,17,Fhad two properties of my own, I had
OL,18,Fsavings, and I was financially stable.
