OL,7,F"Today, I am a single mum working full
OL,8,Ftime, living in rented accommodation,
OL,9,Fwith no savings, trying to make ends
OL,10,Fmeet.
OL,12,F"My mum and dad's peaceful retirement
OL,13,Fhas been stolen from them.
OL,15,F"His impact extends far beyond me. My
OL,16,Fchildren have been silent victims.
